episodes.title: Andrew Mountbatten-Windsor Arrested: Our Reaction | Loose Women
episodes.description:
Royal breaking news this morning as police confirm that former the Prince, now known as Andrew Mountbatten-Windsor, has been arrested on suspicion of misconduct in public office. As officers begin to carry out searches at his addresses in Berkshire and Norfolk, and the King releases a statement, our panel reacts.
